{"tid":2394700,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民眾轉用離線通訊App","createTime":"2021-02-04T10:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T15:14:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cecd9bbe43017307eb5c20c661fa2130e4cac2ed","tid":2394700,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:57:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210204/WHZJDKH4ZBANZMZXXLB5CQXZQM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210204%2FWHZJDKH4ZBANZMZXXLB5CQXZQM%2F&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRG6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=5bfa784c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210204%2FWHZJDKH4ZBANZMZXXLB5CQXZQM%2F&h=4c7dbef8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210204/WHZJDKH4ZBANZMZXXLB5CQXZQM/</a><br />\n<br />\n民眾轉用離線通訊App<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JH4DPyqqhP3reSkT0p5sZge_Y-4=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EZRB7NFTZRDVZDXPNTBE4IFLPQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJH4DPyqqhP3reSkT0p5sZge_Y-4%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEZRB7NFTZRDVZDXPNTBE4IFLPQ.jpg&h=25133170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■近日下載Bridgefy的緬甸用戶大增。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n緬甸軍方周一發起政變和短暫斷網後，離線通訊程式Bridgefy指數小時內下載量逾60萬次，至今已突破100萬次。該公司推文指希望緬甸人民「在艱難的時候可好好利用程式」，正着力改善其保安程序和訊息加密。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n經藍牙傳輸<br />\n<br />\n昂山素姬等政治領袖當日被捕後，最大城市仰光和首都內比都等主要城市一度出現斷網。雖然通訊在晚上恢復，但社運人士隨即在社交網呼籲人民下載Bridgefy，以防再次斷網。該程式利用藍牙技術傳輸，毋須經由互聯網，讓用戶可離線通訊。<br />\n<br />\nBridgefy在2014年由墨西哥的初創公司設立，在全球廣泛使用，尤其在曾對社交網和網絡供應商施加限制的國家。香港2019年反送中運動期間部份地區曾懷疑出現網絡受阻，示威者亦曾使用該程式。該程式同樣用於泰國和尼日利亞的反政府示威，以及土耳其和希臘地震災難現場。程式獲Twitter共同創辦人斯通（Biz Stone）支持，不過網絡安全專家指程式可被入侵，讓用戶有被監視的風險。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"38aba55d38365c352255aa64ed4c9bf8d3ed3ad3","tid":2394700,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:40:42.000Z","msg":"用藍牙傳送咁即係隔幾多距離"},{"pid":"5e364252e9454057fbf9e38dcce1da0fd8d8c6b7","tid":2394700,"uid":359920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38aba55d38365c352255aa64ed4c9bf8d3ed3ad3","tid":2394700,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:40:42.000Z","msg":"用藍牙傳送咁即係隔幾多距離"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T15:14:23.000Z","msg":"可以好遠，因為每個手機裝了 Bridgefy 之後，除了自己通訊，也都是轉播站，可以把訊息接力傳到遠處。"}]}